{"sections":{"main-page":{"type":"main-page","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-center","heading_tag":"h2","text_size":"text-base","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":120,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"image_with_text_overlay_hEnBk9":{"type":"image-with-text-overlay","blocks":{"subheading_k44dQD":{"type":"subheading","disabled":true,"settings":{"subheading":"TITAN LABS","subheading_size":"subtitle-lg","secondary_color":true}},"heading_QpAnek":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"Innovation","heading_size":"title-md","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_8qfXcq":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"text":"<p>At <strong>Titan Labs <\/strong>we don’t just create gear; we create confidence. Our commitment to innovation, protection, and performance ensures you’re always ready for the fight ahead.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["subheading_k44dQD","heading_QpAnek","text_8qfXcq"],"settings":{"transparent_header":false,"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/titan_labs.png","image_height":"adapt","content_width":"small","content_position":"md:items-end md:justify-start","text_alignment":"left","image_mobile":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/header_titan_labs.png","image_height_mobile":"adapt","content_position_mobile":"items-center justify-center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","color_text":"#ffffff","color_highlight":"#e2fb31","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"#171717","color_button_background":"#ffffff","color_button_gradient":"","color_overlay":"#171717","overlay_opacity":9,"padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":true,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"rich_text_w8hb84":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"heading_NwqVhr":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Closing the Innovation Gap in <\/strong><em><strong>Hockey Safety<\/strong><\/em><strong> and Performance<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h2","highlighted_text":"full_text","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["heading_NwqVhr"],"settings":{"text_alignment":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","heading":"","heading_size":"title-md","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":60,"padding_bottom":60,"divider":false,"narrow":true,"rounded":false}},"17371176850bc21c14":{"type":"apps","settings":{"color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false}},"image_with_text_PQQ6Tg":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_VQLyTV":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Not All  Neck Guards Are Created Equal<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_k64AY9":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Ice hockey is one of the fastest and most dangerous sports in the world, yet the gear designed to protect players lags far behind. Most mass-market brands rely on outdated materials for their hockey neck guards, producing overseas in countries like China, and using products like Kevlar® derivatives with cut-resistance ratings of A2 to A3 on the ANSI scale. For a sport where razor-sharp skate blades move at high speeds, this level of protection is dangerously inadequate.<\/p><p>Worse, these products often sacrifice comfort and performance for marginal safety. Stiff, heavy, and lacking stretch, they compromise player mobility—an unacceptable tradeoff in a sport where every second counts.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["heading_VQLyTV","text_k64AY9"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/IMG_65262.jpg","image_height":"500px","image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"300px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"#ffffff","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#171717","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":true,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"image_with_text_rkPQj4":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_eriBxe":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Engineering a Safer Future<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_Er9PWf":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>At <strong>Titan BattleGear<\/strong>, we’ve reimagined hockey safety and performance from the ground up. Leveraging cutting-edge technologies and materials science, we’ve closed the gap, creating gear that doesn’t force players to choose between protection and performance.<br\/><br\/><strong>Advanced Cut-Resistance<\/strong><\/p><p>Our <strong>TITANOTEX™<\/strong> materials are engineered to outperform. Tested on TDM-100 machines, which measure cut resistance using precise and standardized ANSI\/ISEA methods, TITANOTEX achieves ratings up to <strong>A9<\/strong>, the highest cut-resistance level. That’s up to <strong>4x the protection<\/strong> of Kevlar-based products used by competitors.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"image_rUPENC":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ansi_pill.svg","image_width":"custom","image_max_width":700,"image_max_width_mobile":600}}},"block_order":["heading_eriBxe","text_Er9PWf","image_rUPENC"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/schnittpruefung-stfi-dhanus.jpg","image_height":"600px","image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"300px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#f2f2f2","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"image_with_text_Afg8HJ":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"image_e4GfUA":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/arc_guard_logo_10b5d54a-02cd-4230-9122-59e6f443c875.svg","image_width":"custom","image_max_width":500,"image_max_width_mobile":480}},"heading_nijeXb":{"type":"heading","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"<strong>Contoured Collar For Maximum Coverage<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_FCeQhr":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Neck injuries are among the most serious risks in hockey, with jugular and carotid arteries especially vulnerable. Our patented <strong>ARC~GUARD™ collar<\/strong> provides maximum coverage where it matters most, shielding critical areas while maintaining player comfort.<br\/><br\/>Unlike traditional designs, the ARC~GUARD collar:<\/p><ul><li>Slopes under the chin to prevent bunching and irritation.<\/li><li>Stands taller by the ears for enhanced protection.<\/li><li>Offers two tailored versions: <strong>ArcGuard Adapt<\/strong> (stretch collar) and <strong>ArcGuard Adjust<\/strong> (Velcro collar).<\/li><\/ul><p>This combination of comfort and protection ensures players are safer without distraction.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["image_e4GfUA","heading_nijeXb","text_FCeQhr"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/ArcGuard4.png","image_height":"adapt","image_width":"medium","layout":"image_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"300px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"#ffffff","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#00adee","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"image_with_text_VzUieA":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"image_bPgmwd":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/titanotex_logo_0c96e1f0-5bb3-4f3d-acfb-714d8f6d255d.svg","image_width":"custom","image_max_width":500,"image_max_width_mobile":400}},"heading_dKdqei":{"type":"heading","disabled":true,"settings":{"heading":"<strong>Breakthrough Cut-Resistant Materials<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_KcjikM":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<h4><strong>Breakthrough Cut-Resistant Materials<\/strong><\/h4><p>Innovation isn’t just about what’s on the surface—it’s what’s inside. Our gear integrates TITANOTEX materials that:<\/p><p><\/p><ul><li>Maximizes cut resistance while minimizing weight & thickness<\/li><li>Maximizes Thermoregulation to keep players cool under pressure<\/li><li>Strengthens after washing, ensuring cut-protection is not only maintained, but enhanced over time<\/li><\/ul><p>The result? Gear that’s not only safer but actively enhances a player’s performance on the ice.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["image_bPgmwd","heading_dKdqei","text_KcjikM"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/AJ_editado.jpg","image_height":"adapt","image_width":"medium","layout":"text_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"300px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#f2f2f2","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":72,"padding_bottom":72,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"image_with_text_w8xtfU":{"type":"image-with-text","blocks":{"heading_DCXATN":{"type":"heading","settings":{"heading":"<strong>Rejecting the Status Quo<\/strong>","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_tag":"h3","highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"text_gBKMMx":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p>Unlike the mass-market brands produced in Asia with outdated materials, Titan BattleGear is proud to design and produce locally, prioritizing quality over quantity. Our relentless focus on <strong>innovation, protection, and performance<\/strong> ensures that every product we create is built to help players play harder, safer, and longer.<\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-md","text_max_size":32,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}}},"block_order":["heading_DCXATN","text_gBKMMx"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/made_in_colombia.png","image_height":"adapt","image_width":"large","layout":"image_first","text_alignment":"left","content_position":"align-self-center","image_height_mobile":"300px","text_alignment_mobile":"left","color_text":"#171717","color_background":"","gradient_background":"","color_background_2":"#f2f2f2","gradient_background_2":"","color_highlight":"","gradient_highlight":"","color_button_text":"","color_button_background":"","color_button_gradient":"","padding_top":0,"padding_bottom":0,"divider":false,"full_width":false,"rounded":false,"enable_parallax":false,"parallax_direction":"vertical"}},"rich_text_Af9i8J":{"type":"rich-text","blocks":{"text_XzxTJr":{"type":"text","settings":{"text":"<p><strong>Innovation and protection aren’t just our goals; they’re our mission. <\/strong><\/p><p><strong>Dominate the ice with confidence, knowing your safety and performance are unmatched in Titan Battlegear.<\/strong><\/p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"subtext-xl","text_max_size":34,"secondary_color":false,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle"}},"button_9xDDy9":{"type":"button","settings":{"button_label":"Shop Now","button_link":"shopify:\/\/collections","button_size":"md","button_external":false,"button_icon":true}}},"block_order":["text_XzxTJr","button_9xDDy9"],"disabled":true,"settings":{"text_alignment":"center","text_alignment_mobile":"center","heading":"","heading_size":"title-sm","heading_alignment":"text-left md:items-end md:flex-row","heading_width":"small","heading_tag":"h2","subheading":"","description":"","button_label":"","button_link":"","button_external":false,"button_icon":true,"highlighted_text":"none","highlighted_scribble":"circle","color_text":"",